Executive Summary and Problems Encountered 3



Problems encountered:

1. Dataset: Acquiring a high-quality dataset was a significant obstacle. The majority of the datasets I encountered contained gaps that rendered them unsuitable for my purposes. Consequently, I had to scour numerous sources and experiment with various datasets, eventually combining them to produce a single functional dataset that I could work with.

2. DAX Calculations: I encountered challenges in creating a decade-over-decade Power BI measure. Initially, I presumed that the calculation was akin to the year-over-year calculation, but I soon realized that it had distinct differences. I devoted a large amount of time to resolving this particular issue before finally achieving success.

3. GIFs: Creating step-by-step gifs that meet the less than 5MB criteria was a challenging and time-consuming task. To avoid using too many gifs, I had to memorize the steps allowing me to move quickly from one step to the next.
